  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK825">
<l>maṉatti ṉamaiyā tavarai yeṉaittoṉṟuñ</l>
<l>colliṉāṟ ṟēṟaṟpāṟ ṟaṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In nothing whatever is it proper to rely on the words of those who do not love with their heart.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
